# Keep build contexts small and reproducible: never copy host installs, build
# output, secrets, or the generated Prisma client into an image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dev-dist
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
apps/api/src/generated
.git
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
# Non-build inputs — keep them out of the context so a docs/config edit never
# invalidates a build layer (and the context stays small).
docs
.claude
.github
**/*.md
